Touchstartpage.title: Touch Start
Touchstartpage.content: Turn on this option need to click start button when you ready to charge

StartModepage.qrcodecontent: Turn on this option need to scan QR code when you ready to charge.
StartModepage.rfidcontent: Turn on this option and default card will be denied by this charger.
StartModepage.licensecontent: Turn on this option will be allow auto scan car number to start the charging.

Settingpage.bluetoothcontent: Turn on this option allow you configure your device via bluetooth.
Settingpage.wificontent: Turn on this option allow you configure your EV charger to AP point.
Settingpage.ltecontent: Turn on this option allow you configure your EV charger to SIM.

Ocpppage.describe: Please key in the backend address provided to you by E-Faner.
